				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{y}=\frac{{\mathrm{\partial P}}_{\mathrm{pv}}}{{\mathrm{\partial V}}_{\mathrm{pv}}} $$\end{document} to converge to zero [36].

